name: yikmik Spain S.L.
overview:
Yikmik provides a quick and ease to use service that helps connecting people who want to rent a parking place with those renting it. Through Yikmik you can get a return from your parking space in those hours of the day when you are not using it.

For example, when you go to work and your parking place is free, someone might work where you live and need a place to leave the car for a few hours. Or in the event that you drive to a near by city to watch a soccer game, someone in the are might be willing to rent you an space for a few hours. In all those and many other situations, Yikmik helps solve your parking space problem or make some money.
